1.  Check Inputs
2.  Process State (Physics, inputs, ai, etc.)
	a. Apply AI
		i.   Move tank, if possible
		ii.  or turn tank toward player
		iii. or shoot
	b.  Move Player, if button pressed, and possible
	c.  Update bullet position
		i.   Move by velocity
		ii.  If hits tank, restart.
3.  Output Graphics
	a.  Update each tank by the world matrix
	b.  Multiply by projection matrix
	c.  Add to memory for drawing

